QuestData.Title: Fate's Reminder
QuestData.Description:
Fatescribe Roh-Tahl awaits you within Oribos, should you ever wish to change the course of fate.
You may speak with him at your leisure.
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet Fatescribe Roh-Tahl in Oribos if you wish to enter the Threads of Fate.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Meet Fatescribe Roh-Tahl in Oribos to enter the Threads of Fate.
QuestData.RewardText:
You return, mortal.
Do you wish to change your fate?
